`,t.jsx(e.p,{children:"Precise time keeping is essential to mondern industry. Financial services are highly timed, navigation depends on the precise timing of the GPS satellites and we are all following the same time of the network time protocol. And nowadays time is kept with increasingly precise atomic clocks, which are one of the earliest quantum technologies we have. A few reasons which atomic clocks are such marvelous time keepers are:"}),`
`,t.jsxs(e.ul,{children:[`
`,t.jsx(e.li,{children:"No need to get the american, chinese or european atom as they are all equal. Once we agreed with other how we measure time with atoms we all have exactly the tools at hand."}),`
